metadata.name: New Noise
metadata.description:
Inspired by a song by Refused with the same title  
_

How can we expect anyone to listen  
If we are using the same old voice?  
We need new noise  
New art for the real people

We dance to all the wrong songs  
We enjoy all the wrong moves  
We dance to all the wrong songs  
We're not leading  
_

Cut and rearranged CC0 images on a digital canvas, with the addition of some loose drawings, created in Adobe Photoshop  
PNG ⎯ 4000 × 4000 px  
2023
